Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看見敵人的行動軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也許是XRounder的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類大腦中 有一塊掌管特殊能力的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即所謂 X領域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也稱為XRounder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人衝進去想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引敵人機動戰士型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消耗他們的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和高達的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行進路線上的敵人兵力大幅減少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在 天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破加農 準備炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 前方UE艦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊沿途掃清敵人 突入安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 最大戰速！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經數百年宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭終於偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的不明敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二防衛圈被突破也只是時間的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那台機動戰士出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的計劃就一再被打亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該讓它退出歷史舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一台專門為它準備的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是展現XRounder力量的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷8區中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密封系統故障
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認該區狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 應急班緊急出動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸電系統正常 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能沉 在登陸安巴德之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然了得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成靶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來還上次的人情的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛那台機動戰士的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是德西爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 一起來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是擺弄機動戰士的工作適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得不是挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有8台Shaldoll
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來打算送去大部隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我們也算是仁至義盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別沒精打采的 馬上就到後方支援宇域了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是你的老本行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們受傷的機動戰士儘管往我這兒扔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包修包換 立等可取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 艾烏巴的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多禮 保護同志乃當然之舉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來 扎拉姆&艾烏巴的戰士們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多恩·沃伊諾基的在天之靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必會引領我們邁向勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我勒克特·艾法梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和眾多戰友與你們同在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是小孩子的你 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由才不重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是討厭輸給哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肯放我們過去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩吧 盡情地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾應該也不想戰鬥才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 這麼開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你死我活 輸了是會死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 所以戰鬥才開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 還有功夫說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了今天的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備了有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 我的秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音 難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘先生 他們說你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該待在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道我只能看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是實在坐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的話 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有某種不同於我們的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 不可能戰鬥到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很信任他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘中尉 集結殘存機動戰士組成部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能勝任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信我 就還能戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘·德列斯 Genoace出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴 你為什麼會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實也知道我們此行的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括如果拒絕了我們的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會有什麼下場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的力量借給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕是不會被允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說 不這樣的話我就永遠也見不到菲利特了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 我的秘密兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面還有更好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又自己動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 根本不用操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力者之間的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓XRounder的能力成倍增加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你身在此處的唯一原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不過是一台輔助我的機器！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2對1不公平？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對哦 因為Farsia只是我的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 開火Farsia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才剛開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會！碾碎它 Farsia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲的規則不就是打到一方死掉為止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那麼急著結束的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就結束你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是我 贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想…再見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是駕駛機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了見到菲利特 也能忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這到底是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以為見到你就會滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和菲利特在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿了條命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不會有第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾 為什麼把柚鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏是柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了一件活躍氣氛的玩具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命…不是玩具！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有輸 我才沒輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有輸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 沒有輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼…救世主…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我造的高達是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護人類的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連柚鈴也救不了 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180秒後 抵達強行登陸地點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸戰隊待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直搗翼手類的巢穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 交給你和高達了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撬開要塞的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限製器解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁氣眩光系統 最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Dephus
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為地球重力環境下的戰鬥開發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說宇宙空間內的運動性有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟是最新銳最強的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我如何將它駕馭自如
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉·佐伊 Dephus 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我 受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE…我決不會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放過你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:24:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當戰鬥宣告結束時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被詛咒的真相 露出真容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落淚 在宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.73,0:24:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球軌道上方的宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從衛星國家戰爭時代起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了眾多要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE躲藏的安巴德也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被廢棄的宇宙要塞之一

